Julian Day Calculator for Android
About Julian Day please see: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julian_day

This application has the next features:
1) Julian Day Number (JDN) calculation for entered date and vice versa; 
2) A difference in days between two calendar dates calculation;
3) Weekday calculation for entered date.
4) Convertion of Gregorian calendar date to Julian calendar and vice versa 
Dates can be in Gregorian or Julian calendar.